{"tid":789253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幾年後又一條好漢] 港女遭棄屍台灣 男友被控洗黑錢將轉介高院審理","createTime":"2018-08-22T06:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T07:11:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"be5c9eaf3fdb1fd4e8ef55163df3c7a30ca96984","tid":789253,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180822/large/1534912010_a795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180822%2Flarge%2F1534912010_a795.jpg&h=7e4c1072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20歲少女潘曉穎與男友赴台灣度情人節期間被殺，被裝入篋運往草叢棄屍，遇害時已懷孕。男友回港後被揭發涉盜用潘的信用卡，被控盜竊及接贓共4罪。早前控方曾提及考慮控告被告謀殺罪，但今再提訊時只修訂控罪，現控被告4項洗黑錢及3項盜竊交替控罪，案件將於9月10日在東區裁判法院提訊，以轉介高院審理。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月還柙至今的被告陳同佳（19歲）庭上木無表情，聆聽控罪時逐一表示明白。他今續由私人聘請的大狀代表，沒有反對控方就控罪的申請，亦無提出保釋要求。<br />\n<br />\n經修訂及新增控罪包括首項洗黑錢罪，指被告於今年2月17至3月13日處理屬於潘曉穎的銀行提款卡、相機、手機及2萬元台幣。他另3項洗黑錢罪則指他分別於2月19、20及21日處理超過1.9萬元，其餘3項盜竊罪則為後3項洗黑錢罪的交替控罪。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：KTCC534/18】"},{"pid":"bcefd81704c4a6205b98c078a94793261cf342d8","tid":789253,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"最多咪2年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0c1bc8b55209b99795aa413a8cba7b9fd8816f","tid":789253,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"LM睇監都唔使坐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94b6d242df58a956e295f712db8b2c0dac05d61","tid":789253,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗黑錢"},{"pid":"a1e0fe4e8f29baa1ca06b448a447ee1f35fc9318","tid":789253,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e94b6d242df58a956e295f712db8b2c0dac05d61","tid":789253,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗黑錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"我係辯方,會幫佢打 條女授權佢襟錢<br />\n死無對證,疑點利益歸於被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509941006bcee4f59b846bbb04ac7b464ad52b95","tid":789253,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"法律攪佢唔到,最多判2年<br />\n<br />\n最直接就迷暈佢,夾佢上去台灣的漁船,先懲罰到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cec75e684a8c3e1d268bc0c0d100763548b8767","tid":789253,"uid":19654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"法律上告唔到謀殺"},{"pid":"68e5d6dacbef1b424f766d74d177953e45710864","tid":789253,"uid":59040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3da800a2415894a8a36dd26f3cf59c4b49faa7c9","tid":789253,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"叫陳X佳都係大仆街"},{"pid":"f7cc1fec98ca24de6cad045d7294e0217f280662","tid":789253,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e5d6dacbef1b424f766d74d177953e45710864","tid":789253,"uid":59040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:37:38.000Z","msg":"好難夾硬<br />\n判刑有個準則<br />\n<br />\n佢初犯,無可能判最高刑罰"},{"pid":"cf0b2e6a085fc1b459d90c1b97a4bc5eccf570a5","tid":789253,"uid":50595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"68e5d6dacbef1b424f766d74d177953e45710864","tid":789253,"uid":59040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"已咩死姐 淨係有個咁既漏洞比佢走甩謀殺已經法律已死啦"},{"pid":"ce9bbd7be32c3d6916232ed664740234fbcb15cc","tid":789253,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf0b2e6a085fc1b